+\subsection{Cohort manifest}
+
+The frozen review manifest is stored at
+\code{paper_aom/review/cohort_manifest.csv}.  It contains 78 source rows:
+61 regression rows and 17 classification rows.  For primary paired analyses,
+the effective cohort is 60 regression datasets plus 16 classification
+datasets: the QUARTZ regression row is retained for absolute-error and failure
+tables but excluded from ratio summaries because the reference denominator is
+near zero, and one classification row is excluded because source files are
+missing.  The companion denominator document
+\code{paper_aom/review/cohort_manifest.md} records the gates for TabPFN-allowed
+subsets and AOM-Ridge-global allowability.
+
