+
+- AOM-PLS paper provisional: median RMSEP/PLS `0.960`, `42/57` wins.
+- Refreshed AOM-PLS multi-seed robustness: median RMSEP/PLS `0.9623`, `37/53` wins after averaging RMSEP across seeds.
